<li>DiLorenzo, Thomas <a href="http://www.cato.org/pubs/handbook/hb105-39.html" class="external text" title="http://www.cato.org/pubs/handbook/hb105-39.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Cato Handbook for Congress</i>, <i>Antitrust</i></a>.</li>
</ul>


